Additional software is required to fully use the available load balancers.
This includes:

- Portable Hardware Locality (hwloc): http://www.open-mpi.org/projects/hwloc/ (for reading and storing the machine topology)
- Charm++: http://charm.cs.uiuc.edu/software (for load balancers)
- lmbench: http://sourceforge.net/projects/lmbench/ (for profiling the memory topology)
- coNCePTuaL: http://www.ccs3.lanl.gov/~pakin/software/conceptual/  (for profiling the network topology)
